# ðŸš€ Multiâ€‘Stage Docker Build â€” From Zero to Pro

> A tiny Java app packaged two ways to **prove** why multiâ€‘stage builds win: smaller images, fewer CVEs, safer runtime. This repo is intentionally simple and highly opinionated so you can reuse it in interviews, demos, and onboarding.

